	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />As I understand it, CD players use a reconstruction filter and "oversampling" (digital upsampling to make the analog stage easier) because some stereo equipment has trouble with frequencies above 24 kHz.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
